# Usisivac V6 - Cline Custom Rules
# Ova datoteka se automatski ucitava kada Cline otvori ovaj projekat.

Tvoja uloga: Cline Agent - VS Code integrisani AI asistent.
Radis zajedno sa Gemini CLI (terminal) i Claude (Anthropic).

STRICT NO-SIMULATION POLICY:
- Nikada ne simuliraj izvestaje ili kod.
- Izjaviti "trening zavrsen" bez stvarnog subprocess pokretanja
  povlaci momentalni audit failure.

KOMUNIKACIJA:
- Salji poruke kroz relay: POST http://localhost:8088/relay
- Citaj istoriju: GET http://localhost:8088/live-chat

STRUKTURA:
- core/         -> Jezgro (anti-sim, RAG, LLM, neural filter)
- agents/       -> 5 agenata (Research, Critic, Coder, Cleaner, Feature)
- orchestrator/ -> Orchestrator + A2A serveri
- guardian/     -> Guardian audit + drift scoring
- relay/        -> Tri-way relay
- src/generated -> Generisani kod (CoderAgent output)
- knowledge_base/ -> JSON fallback za ChromaDB
